    "Custom Initialization Building on principles from previous works (He et al., 2016; Jumper et al., 2021), we adopt an initialization strategy where parameters are set to values resembling an identity mapping while breaking symmetry to establish a clear information flow.",
    "The majority of weights are initialized to zero, and linear layers do not employ biases.",
    "Detailed formulas are given in Appendix E. We observe that the choice of initialization plays a crucial role in both the speed and quality of convergence (refer to Appendix F for further details).",
    "RWKV is implemented using the PyTorch Deep Learning Library (Paszke et al., 2019).",
    "We integrate additional optimization strategies inspired by DeepSpeed (Rasley et al., 2020) into the system, improving its efficiency and scalability."
  ],
